      <title>2023 年美联储运营损失将增至创纪录的 1143 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/fed-s-operating-losses-swelled-to-record-114-3-billion-in-2023</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2023 年，美联储的支出超出其收入 1143 亿美元，这是有史以来最大的运营亏损，迫使美联储在利率居高不下的情况下放弃向财政部汇款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/fed-s-operating-losses-swelled-to-record-114-3-billion-in-2023</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 15:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
